Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.88,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這個墓也僅僅是裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:41.47,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒有遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.13,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}和老師說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.16,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}全都捨棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:48.97,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}一切都在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.16,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}現在這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.17,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}時間到，我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:06.06,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}爸爸
