Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:15.99,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:58.69,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}如何？真嗣君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:03.07,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}雖然左右擔心，見了面也沒甚麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:08.05,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}在家猶豫不決，來了多好
