Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:24.17,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:35.16,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我開動了
