Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:44.00,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那九成人造肉調理之後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:45.99,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}竟然如此美味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:47.57,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}令人驚嘆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:50.12,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真嗣，你隱藏了才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:53.23,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}美里小姐一直都吃的是速食品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.12,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}所以只好我來下廚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:58.30,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真嗣君，下得廚房的男孩很受歡迎的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:23:59.25,Default,NTFS,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}聽到沒
